node.text: Summer is officially here—how are you making the most of it? node.text: Gingham, plaid and stripes never go out of style, but textiles designer Heather Taylor is here to make them feel fresh. Check out her exclusive new collection for  West Elm - link in bio. #HTHxWestElm

node.text: “I like to break the rules and push boundaries,” says designer @sarahshermansamuel. For this Design Challenge build-out, watch as she turns our blank-slate set into a kids’ bedroom-playroom hybrid that goes big on whimsical architectural details, playful pattern-mixing and room for creativity. Tap the link in our bio to get the look and to see more of Sarah's tips for creating an epic, imagination-station kids’ space. #WestElmKids

node.text: For #InternationalWomensDay, West Elm partnered with eight #WestElmLOCAL female designers on a limited-edition, upcycled shower curtain collection to raise money for @herprojectbsr, a collaborative initiative that strives to empower women workers in global supply chains. Shop these curtains and learn more at westelm.com/herproject! #IWD2021  @weareclosedonmondays @vacilandostudios @candiceluter @ren_vois @mollymdesigns @friendofallglass @utilityobjects @k_apostrophe
